{"tid":1817871,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"好想迫自己呃自己開心，可惜做唔到","createTime":"2020-01-09T12:19:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-09T12:31:06.000Z","uid":58316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a869147972dd55d6ee7ef938ee2fbe856085215c","tid":1817871,"uid":58316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T12:19:40.000Z","msg":"望住隻畢業公仔<br />\n每朝返垃圾工<br />\n真係好難說服自己開心<br />\n或者呢個世界<br />\n自己存在係度<br />\n唔會有一日係真正開心<br />\n一諗返以前<br />\n就感慨同不忿自己經歷<br />\n講真<br />\n呢d case通街都係<br />\n人命其實唔值錢<br />\n自己係咪度都冇所謂<br />\n至多老豆老母喊死<br />\n但講真<br />\n呢個世界冇野多<br />\n最多係人<br />\n其實人真係同畜牲一樣<br />\n真係唔好咁認真<br />\n到頭來都係自生自滅"},{"pid":"7f470c53b451e0e332abf13c65423efddb1df522","tid":1817871,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T12:20:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">上前線</span>"},{"pid":"f85a391e25a84450b901306f7b419cfa28260c23","tid":1817871,"uid":286155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T12:26:47.000Z","msg":"所以話身為一個人，獨特性哩樣野好緊要<br />\n你係一個人，但同時你唔剩只係一個人<br />\n你係你"},{"pid":"d5bfcbca69518766644be071d022ed44061238e6","tid":1817871,"uid":331173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T12:29:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=68ORjuHT1og\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D68ORjuHT1og&d=y5xLblNGdgzQkswvdzbF0zQMt3kYY8c646%2Bk6hbI14w%3D&h=34089d0c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=68ORjuHT1og</a>"},{"pid":"6db8d407e8a8c2c3b1a4509a546c07a4594d0f2b","tid":1817871,"uid":331173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T12:31:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UThmnTvDTY0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DUThmnTvDTY0&d=y5xLblNGdgzQkswvdzbF0zQMt3kYY8c646%2Bk6hbI14w%3D&h=1bbbbf94\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch